# Revokes toast advancements for toggling

advancement revoke @a[tag=myriad.toggleable_compendium_advancement] only myriad:compendium/unlock_compendium
advancement revoke @a[tag=myriad.toggleable_compendium_advancement] only myriad:compendium/lock_compendium
tag @a remove myriad.toggleable_compendium_advancement
